To enable the CardDAV plugin, first run the following (depening on the
database you are using):

	MySQL     : mysql -h [db-server-name] -u [user] -p -D roundcubemail < ${PREFIX}/roundcubemail/plugins/carddav/dbinit/mysql.sql
	PostgreSQL: psql -h[db-server-name] -Upostgres  < ${PREFIX}/roundcubemail/plugins/carddav/dbinit/postgres.sql
	SQLite3   : sqlite3 ${PREFIX}/roundcubemail/db/sqlite.db < ${PREFIX}/roundcubemail/plugins/carddav/dbinit/sqlite3.sql

Next, add 'carddav' to the $rcmail_config['plugins'] array in
${PREFIX}/roundcubemail/config/config.inc.php, e.g.,

  $rcmail_config['plugins'] = array("carddav", ...);

You will also need to review the
${PREFIX}/roundcubemail/plugins/carddav/config.inc.php file. 

Finally, connet to RoundCube, go to Settings/Settings/CardDAV and follow
the instructions of the Manager.
